TWITTER UTILS
================================================================================
Author: Minh-Hoang, Nguyen
Date  : 20/03/2012
================================================================================

-----------
How to use:
-----------
run python GUI.py to call interface and use!

-------------
Features:
-------------
	1. Search tweets and store in mysqldb
	2. Post a message to own account
-------------

